name: Shadows Creeping on the World Legacy
desc: All "Crawler" monsters on the field, except "Acid Crawler", gain 300 ATK and DEF. Once per turn: You can Special Summon 1 Level 2 or lower Insect monster from your hand in face-up or face-down Defense Position. When a Flip monster you control is destroyed by battle with an opponent's monster: You can send that opponent's monster to the GY.
